Tapi dia baik-baik saja sekarang.

486
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,640
Baik-baik saja?

487
00:26:02,309 --> 00:26:03,880
Dia mungkin tampak baik-baik saja,

488
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,680
