509
00:27:04,870 --> 00:27:06,440
Tidak ada acara. Kita di rumah.

510
00:27:06,440 --> 00:27:08,110
Ayo masuk dan tidur di ranjang kita.

511
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:09,180
