519
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,930
Apa aku mengelola restoran ayam goreng di rumah?

520
00:27:33,100 --> 00:27:35,600
Kenapa kamu selalu makan ayam goreng di rumahku?

521
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:38,110
Aku tidak bisa langsung pulang.

522
00:27:38,309 --> 00:27:39,539
Aku di bioskop.

523
00:27:39,969 --> 00:27:42,509
