527
00:27:49,450 --> 00:27:51,549
- Ya.
- Seharusnya bilang lebih awal.

528
00:27:51,549 --> 00:27:52,719
Aku bisa pergi bersamamu.

529
00:27:52,719 --> 00:27:54,759
