00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:24,819
Hei, hampir lupa. Kudengar dahulu Ji Won menyukaimu.

542
00:28:24,819 --> 00:28:25,890
Benarkah?

543
00:28:26,690 --> 00:28:29,989
