- Sial. Bukan ini.

565
00:29:29,549 --> 00:29:30,850
Dia tidak punya mata.

566
00:29:30,850 --> 00:29:33,049
- Duduk saja di sana.
- Tolong keluar dengan aman...

567
00:29:33,049 --> 00:29:34,049
Apa itu?

568
00:29:34,049 --> 00:29:36,289
Aku harus ke toilet.

569
00:29:36,289 --> 00:29:38,430
