615
00:31:41,779 --> 00:31:42,819
Ya.

616
00:31:42,819 --> 00:31:44,279
Jangan berharap.

617
00:31:44,279 --> 00:31:46,749
Jika dia menonton filmmu setelah berkali-kali menolakmu,

618
00:31:46,749 --> 00:31:48,360
