00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:05,270
Apa?

635
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:06,640
Benarkah?

636
00:33:06,640 --> 00:33:07,879
Sudah kubilang.

637
00:33:07,879 --> 00:33:09,410
Aku langsung tahu begitu aku masuk.

638
00:33:09,410 --> 00:33:10,450
Itu Lee Jeong Hoon.

639
00:33:10,450 --> 00:33:11,509
Astaga!

640
00:33:11,509 --> 00:33:14,779
